1
00:00:12,541 --> 00:00:14,708
- ( theme music playing )

2
00:00:27,958 --> 00:00:30,833
- ( singing in Japanese )

3
00:01:42,541 --> 00:01:44,500
- Man:
ESCAPING THE TRAPAR LOSS AREA.

4
00:01:44,583 --> 00:01:46,458
BOTH LIFT AND PROPULSION
ARE RETURNING.

5
00:01:46,541 --> 00:01:48,458
- Woman: THE SHIP
WILL STABILIZE SOON.

6
00:01:48,541 --> 00:01:50,125
- WHAT ABOUT THE ENEMY?

7
00:01:50,208 --> 00:01:52,541
- NO SIGNS OF ENEMY SHIPS
WITHIN DETECTABLE RANGE.

8
00:01:52,625 --> 00:01:54,125
- WHAT'S THE STATUS
OF THE END?

9
00:01:54,208 --> 00:01:57,041
- I'M GETTING NO RESPONSE.
- WELL, KEEP TRYING.

10
00:01:57,125 --> 00:02:00,041
DON'T YOU WORRY, MAJOR.
WHEN WE STABILIZE THE SITUATION,

11
00:02:00,125 --> 00:02:02,708
WE'LL IMMEDIATELY GO
AND RECOVER THAT DOLL.

12
00:02:02,791 --> 00:02:04,708
MAJOR SOREL.
- SECURITY WARNING, SIR.

13
00:02:04,791 --> 00:02:06,750
AN OPEN AFT HATCH.
- WHAT?

14
00:02:11,583 --> 00:02:13,500
- SOMEONE'S LAUNCHED ONE
OF THE LIFE BOARDS.

15
00:02:13,583 --> 00:02:15,333
- DAMN IT, HE'S GOING OFF
ON HIS OWN.

16
00:02:28,583 --> 00:02:30,500
- Renton: I KNOW--

17
00:02:30,583 --> 00:02:32,000
I KNOW MY NAME.

18
00:02:32,083 --> 00:02:36,000
THAT'S RIGHT.
MY NAME IS RENTON THURSTON.

19
00:02:36,083 --> 00:02:38,000
I REMEMBER.

20
00:02:39,625 --> 00:02:41,541
DADDY THUMB,

21
00:02:41,625 --> 00:02:43,541
MOMMY FINGER,

22
00:02:43,625 --> 00:02:45,041
BROTHER FINGER,

23
00:02:46,666 --> 00:02:48,541
SISTER.

24
00:02:48,625 --> 00:02:52,291
EUREKA HELD THIS HAND
BACK IN THAT OCEAN.

25
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:56,000
EUREKA.  EUREKA.

26
00:02:56,083 --> 00:02:58,458
EUREKA!

27
00:03:00,583 --> 00:03:02,833
EUREKA.

28
00:03:02,916 --> 00:03:04,791
HEY, NIRVASH.

29
00:03:04,875 --> 00:03:07,291
OPEN YOUR EYES
AND WAKE UP!

30
00:03:09,625 --> 00:03:11,541
HEY, EUREKA,
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

31
00:03:11,625 --> 00:03:12,791
THE GEKKO WILL BE COMING
TO PICK US UP SOON.

32
00:03:12,875 --> 00:03:15,125
JUST HANG ON UNTIL THEN.

33
00:03:22,875 --> 00:03:25,666
THE WAVES ARE PULLING BACK.

34
00:03:28,041 --> 00:03:31,250
WHO THE HELL ARE YOU?

35
00:03:31,333 --> 00:03:34,166
WHO THE HELL WOULD DO ALL
OF THIS TO EUREKA?

36
00:03:41,541 --> 00:03:44,583
I-- I KNOW-- I KNOW YOU.

37
00:03:44,666 --> 00:03:46,333
YOU'RE THAT GIRL.

38
00:03:49,041 --> 00:03:51,166
SO IT WASN'T A DREAM?

39
00:03:51,250 --> 00:03:55,416
BUT WAIT.
MAYBE I'M STILL DREAMING.

40
00:03:55,500 --> 00:03:59,125
- PUT BOTH HANDS BEHIND YOUR
HEAD AND TURN AROUND TO FACE ME.

41
00:03:59,208 --> 00:04:02,291
- HEY, WAIT JUST A MINUTE.
WHAT DID I DO?

42
00:04:02,375 --> 00:04:05,041
- CALM DOWN.
JUST SLOWLY DO WHAT I SAID.

43
00:04:10,083 --> 00:04:12,500
IT'S YOU.
- ( Anemone screaming )

44
00:04:12,583 --> 00:04:15,250
( coughing )

45
00:04:15,333 --> 00:04:17,083
- ( winces )

46
00:04:17,166 --> 00:04:20,833
- EUREKA!
- DON'T EVEN THINK ABOUT MOVING.

47
00:04:23,416 --> 00:04:26,625
- ANEMONE, HOLD ON A MINUTE.
I'LL GIVE YOU THE MEDICATION.

48
00:04:26,708 --> 00:04:29,708
- HURRY UP!
I CAN'T STAND IT ANYMORE.

49
00:04:29,791 --> 00:04:32,458
- EUREKA, ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?
EUREKA.

50
00:04:32,541 --> 00:04:35,958
- ALL RIGHT, ANEMONE,
NOW LIFT YOUR CHIN.

51
00:04:36,041 --> 00:04:38,125
DO IT.
- OW!

52
00:04:38,208 --> 00:04:41,000
- THAT HURT.
- ( sobbing )

53
00:04:42,833 --> 00:04:45,708
DOMINIC, PLEASE.
MY HEAD.  DO SOMETHING.

54
00:04:45,791 --> 00:04:48,541
I CAN'T TAKE IT.
- I DON'T HAVE A SPARE.

55
00:04:48,625 --> 00:04:51,000
COME ON, LET'S GO BACK
TO THE SHIP.

56
00:04:51,083 --> 00:04:54,666
CLIMB OUT.  I'LL HELP YOU.

57
00:04:54,750 --> 00:04:58,666
- DON'T TOUCH ME.
LEAVE ME ALONE!

58
00:04:58,750 --> 00:05:01,333
COME ON, DOMINIC, HURRY!

59
00:05:01,416 --> 00:05:03,208
WHY ARE YOU STANDING THERE?
DO SOMETHING.

60
00:05:03,291 --> 00:05:05,416
DO SOMETHING ABOUT
THIS HEAD OF MINE!

61
00:05:10,541 --> 00:05:14,208
- ( grunting )
ALL RIGHT, HERE WE GO.

62
00:05:14,291 --> 00:05:17,666
- THE CLOSEST TOWN
IS SALISA ORNE.

63
00:05:17,750 --> 00:05:19,333
IF WE CAN FIND
A GOVERNMENT-RUN HOSPITAL,

64
00:05:19,416 --> 00:05:22,541
I'M SURE WE'LL FIND
THE MEDICINE YOU NEED.

65
00:05:22,625 --> 00:05:24,875
YOU JUST LAY HERE FOR A WHILE.
TRY TO REST.

66
00:05:24,958 --> 00:05:27,083
I'LL BE RIGHT BACK.

67
00:05:27,166 --> 00:05:30,208
- IF I KNEW IT WAS GOING TO
END UP LIKE THIS,

68
00:05:30,291 --> 00:05:32,375
I SHOULD LEAVE EUREKA
AND GO GET HELP.

69
00:05:36,666 --> 00:05:39,583
HOLD ON JUST A MINUTE.
I'LL BE RIGHT BACK.

70
00:05:39,666 --> 00:05:43,583
- WHO ARE YOU?  YOU'RE IN MY
WAY.  HURRY UP AND MOVE.

71
00:05:43,666 --> 00:05:45,333
- I WANT YOU
TO TAKE ME WITH YOU.

72
00:05:45,416 --> 00:05:48,083
- WHAT A PEST.
GO AWAY.

73
00:05:48,166 --> 00:05:50,583
- IF YOU REFUSE
TO TAKE ME WITH YOU--

74
00:05:50,666 --> 00:05:52,916
- YEAH, WHAT?

75
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:56,583
- SHOOT ME.  YOU'RE NOT GETTING
AWAY FROM HERE ANYWAY.

76
00:05:56,666 --> 00:05:58,125
- WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

77
00:06:00,250 --> 00:06:02,416
- YOU MISSING THIS?

78
00:06:02,500 --> 00:06:06,541
- ( screams )
WHEN THE HELL DID YOU--

79
00:06:06,625 --> 00:06:09,041
ALL RIGHT,
THAT'S ENOUGH FOOLING AROUND.

80
00:06:11,708 --> 00:06:13,791
I REALLY WILL SHOOT,
YOU KNOW?

81
00:06:15,250 --> 00:06:16,250
- GO AHEAD.
- I WILL.

82
00:06:18,708 --> 00:06:20,500
- I'M PRETTY SURE YOU
DON'T KNOW HOW TO FIX THIS.

83
00:06:20,583 --> 00:06:22,958
- WHAT?  THE MUFFLER?!

84
00:06:23,041 --> 00:06:26,208
DAMN IT,
WHEN THE HELL DID HE--

85
00:06:26,291 --> 00:06:28,708
- I CAN FIX IT.
BUT IN RETURN,

86
00:06:28,791 --> 00:06:30,916
YOU HAVE TO TAKE ME ALONG.

87
00:06:34,041 --> 00:06:36,666
- FINE.  HURRY UP.
WE DON'T HAVE MUCH TIME.

88
00:06:36,750 --> 00:06:39,916
- Woman: TypeZERO IS STILL
MAINTAINING SILENCE.

89
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:42,625
AND RENTON'S VITAL SIGNS
HAVE DISAPPEARED.

90
00:06:42,708 --> 00:06:45,958
- WOZ, CONFIRM WITH JOBS WHETHER
OR NOT WE CAN LAUNCH THE 909.

91
00:06:46,041 --> 00:06:49,000
- OKAY.
- TALHO, TAKE US DOWN

92
00:06:49,083 --> 00:06:51,666
TO A LOWER ALTITUDE.
- THERE ARE NO WAVES OUT THERE.

93
00:06:51,750 --> 00:06:53,666
IT'S IMPOSSIBLE TO USE AN LFO.

94
00:06:53,750 --> 00:06:55,666
- IF I GO IN VEHICLE MODE,
I WON'T HAVE TO DEAL WITH THAT.

95
00:06:55,750 --> 00:06:58,666
- AND HOW MANY HOURS DO YOU
THINK THAT'S GONNA TAKE?

96
00:06:58,750 --> 00:07:02,666
- THE MILITARY KLF WENT DOWN
RIGHT ALONGSIDE THE NIRVASH.

97
00:07:02,750 --> 00:07:05,666
- SO WE CAN ASSUME THEY'LL BE
SENDING DOWN A RETRIEVAL TEAM.

98
00:07:05,750 --> 00:07:08,250
THE WORST CASE SCENARIO IS

99
00:07:08,333 --> 00:07:09,666
WE RUN INTO THEM DOWN THERE.

100
00:07:09,750 --> 00:07:11,916
- THAT'S ALL THE MORE
REASON TO GO.

101
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:15,666
WE CAN'T AFFORD TO HAND THOSE
TWO AND NIRVASH TO THE MILITARY.

102
00:07:15,750 --> 00:07:18,666
SO AM I MISTAKEN
ABOUT ANY OF THAT?

103
00:07:18,750 --> 00:07:21,291
- NO, YOU'RE NOT
MISTAKEN, BUT--

104
00:07:21,375 --> 00:07:22,666
- THEN IT'S TIME TO GO.

105
00:07:22,750 --> 00:07:24,666
- I'M TELLING YOU,
IT'S REALLY DANGEROUS.

106
00:07:24,750 --> 00:07:28,166
HOW DO YOU THINK YOU'RE GONNA
GET THERE WITHOUT THE GEKKO?

107
00:07:28,250 --> 00:07:30,166
HEY, COME BACK,
HOLD ON RIGHT THERE!

108
00:07:31,791 --> 00:07:34,208
- I DID TELL YOU TO FIX IT,

109
00:07:34,291 --> 00:07:37,708
BUT I NEVER SAID ONE WORD ABOUT
TUNING IT TO RUN THIS LOUD.

110
00:07:37,791 --> 00:07:40,916
- GOTTA HURRY, 'CAUSE IF WE
DON'T, EUREKA WILL BE--

111
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:43,250
THAT GIRL, WHO IS SHE?

112
00:07:43,333 --> 00:07:45,541
COME ON, PLEASE, TELL ME.

113
00:07:45,625 --> 00:07:49,125
THAT KLF.  WHY DOES IT LOOK
SO MUCH LIKE THE NIRVASH?

114
00:07:49,208 --> 00:07:50,708
- I HAVE NO NEED
TO ANSWER THAT.

115
00:07:50,791 --> 00:07:53,375
- YES, YOU DO.  IT'S BECAUSE
OF HER THAT EUREKA'S HURT.

116
00:07:53,458 --> 00:07:55,250
- WHAT ABOUT YOU?
DO YOU HAVE ANY IDEA

117
00:07:55,333 --> 00:07:57,083
WHAT YOU GUYS WERE REALLY
TRYING TO DO UP THERE?

118
00:07:57,166 --> 00:08:01,208
- YOU MEAN THE MILITARY KNOWS?
YOU KNOW WHAT THAT HUGE CLOUD,

119
00:08:01,291 --> 00:08:04,375
CALLED A CORALIAN IS?  YOU KNOW
WHAT THAT THING IS ALL ABOUT?

120
00:08:04,458 --> 00:08:07,041
- WAIT A MINUTE.
WHERE DID YOU HEAR THAT?

121
00:08:07,125 --> 00:08:09,875
WHO TOLD YOU THAT NAME?
- HEY, WATCH WHERE YOU'RE GOING.

122
00:08:09,958 --> 00:08:11,750
- HUH?  WHOA!

123
00:08:11,833 --> 00:08:13,125
- ( brakes screech )

124
00:08:21,500 --> 00:08:24,291
- HUH?
- WHO DID YOU HEAR IT FROM?

125
00:08:25,875 --> 00:08:27,750
WHO DID YOU HEAR
THE NAME CORALIAN FROM?

126
00:08:27,833 --> 00:08:29,833
- IS IT BAD FOR ME
TO KNOW THAT?

127
00:08:29,916 --> 00:08:32,208
- ON YOUR FEET.

128
00:08:35,833 --> 00:08:38,958
- SO WHAT IN THE WORLD
IS A CORALIAN?

129
00:08:40,666 --> 00:08:43,208
- ( gasps )

130
00:08:43,291 --> 00:08:46,750
IT'S GONE.
WAIT.  DID I DROP IT?

131
00:08:46,833 --> 00:08:48,500
WHERE'D IT GO?

132
00:08:48,583 --> 00:08:50,583
DON'T TELL ME YOU
DID IT AGAIN?

133
00:08:50,666 --> 00:08:52,833
- YOU MEAN THAT OVER THERE?

134
00:08:55,583 --> 00:08:58,500
- LOWER IT SLOWLY, OKAY?
ON THREE.

135
00:08:58,583 --> 00:09:01,208
- COME ON, TELL ME.
I WANNA KNOW WHAT A CORALIAN IS.

136
00:09:01,291 --> 00:09:03,625
- I TOLD YOU.
I HAVE NO NEED TO ANSWER.

137
00:09:03,708 --> 00:09:05,500
- IT BOTHERS ME, OKAY?

138
00:09:05,583 --> 00:09:07,500
WHEN I ENTERED THAT CLOUD,

139
00:09:07,583 --> 00:09:11,250
I FELT LIKE I WASN'T
MYSELF ANYMORE.  BUTTERFLIES.

140
00:09:11,333 --> 00:09:13,500
- ENOUGH WITH
THE DAMN BUTTERFLIES.

141
00:09:13,583 --> 00:09:15,958
- OH, AND IT FEELS LIKE
I GOTTA PEE MY PANTS.

142
00:09:16,041 --> 00:09:18,125
( urinating )
- ( sighs )

143
00:09:18,208 --> 00:09:21,166
- THERE'S ONE THING THAT
I'D LIKE TO CONFIRM RIGHT NOW.

144
00:09:21,250 --> 00:09:23,500
WHAT YOU TOLD ME EARLIER.

145
00:09:23,583 --> 00:09:26,166
YOU ENTERED INTO THE ZONE,
DIDN'T YOU?

146
00:09:31,208 --> 00:09:33,333
- ( engine revving )

147
00:09:33,416 --> 00:09:35,625
- GET ON.  TIME'S SHORT.

148
00:09:35,708 --> 00:09:38,875
- Man: ATTENTION ALL REMAINING
CITIZENS IN THE AREA.

149
00:09:38,958 --> 00:09:40,708
YOU ARE TO EVACUATE IMMEDIATELY

150
00:09:40,791 --> 00:09:41,958
TO YOUR NEAREST
COMMUNITY CENTER.

151
00:09:42,041 --> 00:09:44,833
THERE ARE NO SCHEDULED TIMES
OR DATES AS TO

152
00:09:44,916 --> 00:09:48,458
WHEN THE WATER, GAS
AND ELECTRICITY WILL RESUME.

153
00:09:48,541 --> 00:09:50,708
- GET THE MAP FILE.
- HUH?

154
00:09:50,791 --> 00:09:52,041
- THERE'S ONE THERE
UNDER YOUR FEET.

155
00:09:52,125 --> 00:09:54,375
HURRY UP AND FIND A HOSPITAL.

156
00:09:57,625 --> 00:09:59,208
- I GUESS THIS IS IT.

157
00:09:59,291 --> 00:10:02,333
SALISA ORNE.

158
00:10:02,416 --> 00:10:04,708
WHERE IS IT?
SALISA ORNE.

159
00:10:04,791 --> 00:10:08,208
OH.  "SALPO MALOO?"
NO, THAT'S WRONG.

160
00:10:08,291 --> 00:10:10,625
- OH, GIVE ME THAT!
- ( grunts )

161
00:10:13,625 --> 00:10:15,083
- WHERE'S NORTH?

162
00:10:15,166 --> 00:10:17,041
TELL ME WHICH WAY
NORTH IS ON THIS MAP.

163
00:10:17,125 --> 00:10:18,416
- NORTH IS ALWAYS UP.

164
00:10:18,500 --> 00:10:20,791
AND BY THE WAY,
YOU'VE GOT IT REVERSED.

165
00:10:20,875 --> 00:10:23,750
- IT'S UP?  REVERSED?  WHERE?

166
00:10:23,833 --> 00:10:26,958
- OH, BROTHER,
HE'S SERIOUSLY NUTS.

167
00:10:31,166 --> 00:10:33,833
- DISGUSTING WORTHLESS SOLDIER!
- OH!

168
00:10:41,250 --> 00:10:43,375
- ( blows raspberries )
- ( engine turns over )

169
00:10:43,458 --> 00:10:44,875
- HOLD ON TIGHT.

170
00:10:44,958 --> 00:10:47,125
WE'RE GETTING OUT OF THE MAIN
PART OF TOWN FOR NOW.

171
00:10:51,208 --> 00:10:52,583
- ( panting )

172
00:10:54,208 --> 00:10:57,958
THE SIGNS ARE ALL COVERED
IN GRAFFITI.  I CAN'T READ 'EM.

173
00:11:00,208 --> 00:11:02,000
- NO GOOD.

174
00:11:03,500 --> 00:11:06,416
THIS SLUMMY TOWN IS BUILT
LIKE SOME DARK LABYRINTH.

175
00:11:06,500 --> 00:11:09,125
EVEN THE KIDS HERE
ARE LOWLIFES.

176
00:11:09,208 --> 00:11:10,958
- SO WHAT DO WE DO NOW?

177
00:11:11,041 --> 00:11:14,458
EVEN IF WE WANTED TO ASK FOR
DIRECTIONS, THERE'S NO ONE HERE.

178
00:11:19,708 --> 00:11:22,958
BUT THERE'S NO WAY.

179
00:11:23,041 --> 00:11:26,666
THE CORALIAN COULDN'T HAVE
CAUSED THIS, NOT THIS MUCH.

180
00:11:26,750 --> 00:11:28,833
"MILITIA MEMORIAL HOSPITAL.

181
00:11:28,916 --> 00:11:31,125
ON WEST STREET
IN THE 7th DISTRICT."

182
00:11:31,208 --> 00:11:33,125
- Man: YOU'RE SAYING IT WAS
ABNORMAL WEATHER?

183
00:11:33,208 --> 00:11:34,708
- Sorel:
I CAN'T ANSWER THAT QUESTION.

184
00:11:34,791 --> 00:11:37,625
- THERE ARE MORE TECTONIC
SHIFTS HAPPENING NOW.

185
00:11:37,708 --> 00:11:39,833
IT HAD SOMETHING TO DO WITH
THAT GIANT CLOUD, DIDN'T IT?

186
00:11:39,916 --> 00:11:41,708
- WE'RE INVESTIGATING THAT.

187
00:11:41,791 --> 00:11:44,000
NOW LET GO OF ME.

188
00:11:44,083 --> 00:11:47,666
- THAT'S WHAT YOU PEOPLE SAY
EVERY TIME WE ASK YOU SOMETHING.

189
00:11:47,750 --> 00:11:50,291
WHAT KIND OF PEOPLE ARE YOU
IN THE MILITARY?

190
00:11:50,375 --> 00:11:53,666
- THE PURPOSE OF OUR EXISTENCE
IS TO PROTECT CIVILIANS.

191
00:11:53,750 --> 00:11:56,000
- QUIT THAT JOKE
YOU'RE TELLING THERE.

192
00:11:56,083 --> 00:11:58,791
- THE TOWN'S DESTROYED.
YOU SAW IT WITH YOUR OWN EYES.

193
00:11:58,875 --> 00:12:01,291
AND IT'S THANKS TO YOU GUYS
IN THE MILITARY.

194
00:12:01,375 --> 00:12:04,333
- DAMN YOU TO HELL!

195
00:12:05,875 --> 00:12:07,666
- DAMN.

196
00:12:07,750 --> 00:12:09,833
YOU LOUSY GOOD-FOR-NOTHING
TRAITOR.

197
00:12:09,916 --> 00:12:12,958
- WHAT DO YOU GUYS
THINK YOU'RE DOING?

198
00:12:13,041 --> 00:12:16,166
THIS IS NO TIME TO BE FIGHTING
OVER SOMETHING STUPID.

199
00:12:16,250 --> 00:12:19,166
WE'VE GOTTA GET GOING.  I FOUND
THE LOCATION OF THE HOSPITAL.

200
00:12:19,250 --> 00:12:20,625
- THIS KID'S ONE OF YOUR GUYS?

201
00:12:20,708 --> 00:12:23,333
- YEAH, THAT'S RIGHT.
YOU WANNA MAKE SOMETHING OF IT?

202
00:12:23,416 --> 00:12:26,750
- IN THAT CASE,
WE NEED TO GIVE HIM OUR THANKS.

203
00:12:29,916 --> 00:12:32,833
- HEY, DO THINGS LIKE THAT
HAPPEN TO YOU A LOT?

204
00:12:32,916 --> 00:12:35,833
- SHUT UP.  IF YOU FOUND
THE LOCATION OF A HOSPITAL,

205
00:12:35,916 --> 00:12:37,833
YOU COULD HAVE JUST GONE
ON THERE ALONE, YOU KNOW?

206
00:12:37,916 --> 00:12:40,833
- YOU NEVER TOLD ME WHAT KIND
OF MEDICINES THAT YOU NEEDED.

207
00:12:40,916 --> 00:12:42,833
ANYWAY, HEAD WEST.

208
00:12:42,916 --> 00:12:47,666
YOU KNOW, YOU COULD AT LEAST
GIVE ME ONE WORD OF THANKS.

209
00:12:49,916 --> 00:12:52,333
I KEEP TELLING YOU
WE GOTTA GO WEST.

210
00:12:52,416 --> 00:12:56,833
- SORRY,
BUT IS WEST THE DIRECTION

211
00:12:56,916 --> 00:12:58,333
OF THE HAND YOU HOLD
YOUR FORK WITH?

212
00:12:58,416 --> 00:13:00,791
- THIS GUY IS REALLY NUTS.

213
00:13:08,958 --> 00:13:10,875
- WHO MAY I ASK ARE YOU TWO?

214
00:13:10,958 --> 00:13:13,875
- JUST DISPENSE THE MEDICATION
EXACTLY AS YOU SEE ON THAT NOTE.

215
00:13:13,958 --> 00:13:16,541
- HEY, HOW MANY PATIENTS
ARE YOU TREATING?

216
00:13:16,625 --> 00:13:17,875
- TWO.

217
00:13:17,958 --> 00:13:19,541
- YOU'D KILL BOTH OF THEM
WITH THIS MUCH.

218
00:13:19,625 --> 00:13:21,208
- THIS IS NONE
OF YOUR CONCERN.

219
00:13:21,291 --> 00:13:23,875
THE INTELLIGENCE DEPARTMENT WILL
SEND THE OFFICIAL DOCUMENTS.

220
00:13:23,958 --> 00:13:25,833
AND DON'T ASK ME WHY.

221
00:13:25,916 --> 00:13:28,500
JUST SHUT UP
AND GIVE ME THE PRESCRIPTION.

222
