295
00:18:24,250 --> 00:18:27,166
- THE SOURCE IS RIGHT WHERE
THE CORALIAN WAS.

296
00:18:27,250 --> 00:18:30,250
- WHAT DID YOU SAY?
OH, MY!

297
00:18:30,333 --> 00:18:33,208
